{
  "stem": "10768.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Sambor, of course, was not destroyed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "You know, the Polish were-- the Polish people, Polish soldiers were running, the army was running very deep.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And the German came in without any resistance.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And after a week, Irene, her husband, the nephew and niece decided to go back to Lesko from Sambor.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And when they came to a town, which is about 15 kilometer from our town, the town is called Ustrzyki.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And they slept over in, in Ustrzyki, to find out how the situation is in Lesko.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Because Lesko was on the river San.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "It was more dangerous, they were not-- they wanted to find out how the story is.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "In the middle of the night, there's a knock at the door.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "They took out the two men-- Irene's husband and Irene's nephew-- and the owner of the person where they were sleeping.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And without any reasons, they were shot to death.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By Germans, by Germans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is according to Irene's-- Irene was hidden by Dr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] later on.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was in Lesko, in our town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was hidden by Dr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] together with two of her friends, who were also professionals.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He really offered his life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He paid eight-- that she was helping them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And while the three girls survived hidden in a hospital on an attic, where he had a big sign, that this is the epidemiology apartment, nobody should come here, they three survived.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the two of them were on very high position in Israel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Irene survived, and she also became-- she was a nurse.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she was a nurse-- she later came to the United States.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "To tell you, she married Dr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was promising her that he would come to United States.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
